Distribution. Known from Mozambique , South Africa , and Western Australia in the Indian Ocean, and Wallis and Futuna , and Japan in the western Pacific Ocean, at depths of 714–1,750 m ( Cohen and Nielsen 1978 ; Shcherbachev 1980 ;
Williams et al. 1996
; Nielsen and Cohen 1999 ; J. G. Nielsen pers. comm.; this study) ( Fig. 4 ).
